sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Dev as Usuario
    participant Compose as Docker Compose
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant API as API FastAPI
    participant Web as Dashboard SvelteKit

    Dev->>Compose: docker compose up --build
    Compose->>DB: iniciar postgres:16-alpine
    DB-->>Compose: healthcheck pg_isready OK
    Compose->>API: construir e iniciar contenedor api
    API->>DB: alembic upgrade head
    API->>API: generate_dataset.py --size 2000 --seed 42
    API->>DB: load_dataset.py carga alarmas y rechazos
    API-->>Compose: healthcheck /api/v1/health OK
    Compose->>Web: construir e iniciar contenedor web
    Web->>API: consulta SSR a /api/v1/alarms y /metrics
    API->>DB: ejecutar consultas filtradas y agregadas
    DB-->>API: resultados SQL
    API-->>Web: JSON paginado y metricas
    Web-->>Dev: dashboard en http://localhost:3000
